<typename XMsgT>create_subscriptions(X_input_topics, &m_X_subs, &FilterNode::X_callback)
in: X_input_topics - this is a vector with FrameIds of sensors of type X (e.g. odom_input_topics created while parsing)
inout: &m_X_subs - subscriptions_vector member that has to be changed (e.g. m_odom_subs)
in: &FilterNode::X_callback - function pointer to one of callback methods (odom/pose/twist/imu_callback)
Explicit instantiation for each messge_typ (for the example of odom)
